    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 911 Carrera features the high-revving 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant is mechanically robust, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and updated rear main seal. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for exceptional lateral grip. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the chassis rigidity and throttle synchronization are impeccable. Includes a comprehensive service log detailing consistent fluid intervals and cooling system refreshes.",
