    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scratch near the driver-side door handle\u2014standard for its age. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and entirely smoke-free. The upholstery shows light signs of use on the entry bolsters but remains free of rips or stains, and all power features, including the sunroof and infotainment system, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts are crisp, and there are no dashboard warning lights. I have kept a detailed log of all maintenance, including a recent oil service and a fresh set of brake pads. The tires provide ample grip with plenty of life left in the tread. This is a dependable, honest car that is ready to be driven home today.",
