      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable daily driver and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape, super dependable, and honestly just a blast to drive. I've taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you right away! If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s solid and well-maintained without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
